# Cocktail Sauce

> A fresh and tangy cocktail sauce perfect for shrimp. #seafood #sauce #american

- Chili Sauce | 1 cup | 
- Horseradish | Prepared, 2 tbsp | 
- Lemon | 1/2 | Juiced
- Tobasco Sauce | 1 tsp, adjust to taste  | 
- Salt | Pinch | 

In a bowl, mix together chili sauce, horseradish, freshly squeezed lemon juice, and hot sauce. Season with salt and black pepper.

Serve the cocktail sauce chilled with shrimp.
